name: KIDROBOT MUNNY IPOD / PC SPEAKER SYSTEM CUSTOM
description:
this is a 3 piece speakers system which has been fitted into 3 munnys (1X 7inch & 2X 4 inch) it works on both my ipod and pc on a normal jack connection. It took about a week for all the carving to be done and to mount the speakers.

It was sprayed using ironlak black, gold and red this paints mad gloss finish has made the figures ultra shiny!

Any more question please contact me

(Iphone NOT included)
